<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html, body {
        height: 100%; /* Sayfanın tamamının yüksekliğini kapsar */
        margin: 0; /* Varsayılan margin'i kaldırır */
        background-color: #e6e6e6; /* İstenilen arka plan rengi */
        }
        .accordion-content {
            transition: max-height 0.5s ease, opacity 0.5s ease;
            opacity: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-height: 0;
        }

        .accordion-content.show {
            opacity: 1;
            max-height: 1000px; /* Yeterince büyük bir değer veriyoruz ki içerik görünür hale gelsin */
        }

        .accordion-toggle .arrow {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .accordion-toggle.active .arrow {
            transform: rotate(180deg); /* Aşağı bakıyorken yukarı döndür */
        }
    </style>
    <title>FAQ</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include(navbar) %>
    <section class="py-24">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-x-16 gap-y-5 xl:gap-28 lg:flex-row lg:justify-between max-lg:max-w-2xl mx-auto max-w-full">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                    <img src="https://pagedone.io/asset/uploads/1696230182.png" alt="FAQ tailwind section" class="w-full rounded-xl object-cover" />
                </div>
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                    <div class="lg:max-w-xl">
                        <div class="mb-6 lg:mb-16">
                            <h6 class="text-lg text-center font-bold text-green-500 mb-2 lg:text-left">Frequently Asked Questions</h6>
                            <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-bold text-gray-900 leading-[3.25rem] mb-5 lg:text-left">Looking for answers?</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion py-8  p-4 border-b border-solid border-gray-200 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg min-h-24 flex flex-col justify-between my-4">
                            <button class="accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center justify-between text-xl font-normal leading-8 text-gray-600 w-full transition duration-500 hover:text-indigo-600" aria-controls="basic-collapse-one">
                                <h5>How to create an account?</h5>
                                <svg class="arrow text-gray-900 transition duration-500 group-hover:text-indigo-600" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                    <path d="M16.5 8.25L12.4142 12.3358C11.7475 13.0025 11.4142 13.3358 11 13.3358C10.5858 13.3358 10.2525 13.0025 9.58579 12.3358L5.5 8.25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                            <div id="basic-collapse-one" class="accordion-content" aria-labelledby="basic-heading-one">
                                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-600">To create an account, find the 'Sign up' button and fill out the registration form with your personal information, and click 'Register'.Then log in to start using the platform.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                            <div class="accordion py-8  p-4 border-b border-solid border-gray-200 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg min-h-24 flex flex-col justify-between my-4">
                                <button class="accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center justify-between font-normal text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600 w-full transition duration-500 hover:text-indigo-600" aria-controls="basic-collapse-two">
                                    <h5>How can I create a slide?</h5>
                                    <svg class="arrow text-gray-900 transition duration-500 group-hover:text-indigo-600" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                        <path d="M16.5 8.25L12.4142 12.3358C11.7475 13.0025 11.4142 13.3358 11 13.3358C10.5858 13.3358 10.2525 13.0025 9.58579 12.3358L5.5 8.25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </button>
                                <div id="basic-collapse-two" class="accordion-content" aria-labelledby="basic-heading-two">
                                    <p class="text-base text-gray-500 font-normal">To create a slide, you first need to create an account if you don't have one. After setting up your account, log in and go to your profile. In your profile, click on the "Slide Generation" section on the left side. Next, fill in the "Title" and "Description" fields. Then, select the theme you want to use and finally upload your PDF files. Once you have entered all the information, click the "Generate" button to create your slides. By following these steps, your slides will be added to your profile.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion py-8  p-4 border-b border-solid border-gray-200 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg min-h-24 flex flex-col justify-between my-4">
                                <button class="accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center justify-between text-xl font-normal leading-8 text-gray-600 w-full transition duration-500 hover:text-indigo-600" aria-controls="basic-collapse-three">
                                    <h5> What do "Creating" and "Evaluating" mean?</h5>
                                    <svg class="arrow text-gray-900 transition duration-500 group-hover:text-indigo-600" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                        <path d="M16.5 8.25L12.4142 12.3358C11.7475 13.0025 11.4142 13.3358 11 13.3358C10.5858 13.3358 10.2525 13.0025 9.58579 12.3358L5.5 8.25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </button>
                                <div id="basic-collapse-three" class="accordion-content" aria-labelledby="basic-heading-three">
                                    <p class="text-base text-gray-500 font-normal">The terms "Creating" and "Evaluating" represent specific stages in the slide creation process. While your slide is being generated in the background, the "Download" button displays the word "Creating." This indicates that your slide content is in the preparation stage. Then, as the slide content moves to the application phase, the label changes to "Evaluating." At this stage, the system is assessing the slide you created and making necessary adjustments. Finally, when your slide is ready, the "Download" button appears, meaning you can download and use your slide.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion py-8 p-4 border-b border-solid border-gray-200 bg-gray-300 rounded-lg min-h-24 flex flex-col justify-between my-4">
                                <button class="accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center justify-between text-xl font-normal leading-8 text-gray-600 w-full transition duration-500 hover:text-indigo-600" aria-controls="basic-collapse-four">
                                    <h5>Why can't I review the slides in the Slide Hub?</h5>
                                    <svg class="arrow text-gray-900 transition duration-500 group-hover:text-indigo-600" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                        <path d="M16.5 8.25L12.4142 12.3358C11.7475 13.0025 11.4142 13.3358 11 13.3358C10.5858 13.3358 10.2525 13.0025 9.58579 12.3358L5.5 8.25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </button>
                                <div id="basic-collapse-four" class="accordion-content" aria-labelledby="basic-heading-four">
                                    <p class="text-base text-gray-500 font-normal">You need to log in to your account in order to review the slides in the Slide Hub. Once you are logged in, you can explore the slides and download those that interest you. Please remember that the Slide Hub displays only the slides that users have published publicly.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-toggle').forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const accordionContent = button.nextElementSibling;
                const isActive = button.classList.toggle('active');

                // Tüm diğer accordion'ları kapat
                document.querySelectorAll('.accordion-content').forEach(content => {
                    if (content !== accordionContent) {
                        content.style.maxHeight = '0';
                        content.classList.remove('show');
                        content.previousElementSibling.classList.remove('active'); // Toggle butonunu kapat
                    }
                });

                if (isActive) {
                    accordionContent.style.maxHeight = accordionContent.scrollHeight + 'px'; // Açık yükseklik
                    accordionContent.classList.add('show');
                } else {
                    accordionContent.style.maxHeight = '0'; // Kapatma yüksekliği
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        accordionContent.classList.remove('show');
                    }, 300); // Kapatma animasyonu süresi
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
    <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>
